Screenshots: N/A

Modem Configuration Page Address(es): None

Modem Default IP Address(es): N/A

Connection Types:

Ethernet

USB

Status Lights:

POWER

Solid Green - The modem has power

Off - The modem is without power, make certain that the modem is plugged into a working power outlet

CABLE

Solid Green - The modem is connected and registered on the network

Slow Blinking Green - The modem has found a downstream signal and is attempting to register on the network

Fast Blinking Green - Modem registration is in progress

Off - No downstream signal found

PC

Solid Green - A PC is connected to the modem

Off - No PC has been detected as being connectd to the modem

DATA

Blinking Green - Your cable modem is sending or receiving data

Off - There is currently no activity on your connection

TEST

Flashing Green - The modem is downloading software or a self test is in progress

Solid Green - The self test failed, try powercycling the modem

Off - No test in progress

Misc Notes:

N/A
